)","displayOrder":0,"co2":0.000000000000000000,"eeoi":0.000000000000000000,"aer":0.000000000000000000,"soxMt":0.000000000000000000,"sox":0.000000000000000000,"noxMt":0.000000000000000000,"nox":0.000000000000000000,"euEtsDetails":{"allowancePurchases":null,"eua":0.000000000000000000,"euaCostUSD":null,"euaCostEUR":null,"euaPriceUSD":null,"euaPriceEUR":null,"euaVerified":null,"euaEstimated":null,"euaPurchased":null,"euaBalance":null}}]},"remarkList":[{"modifiedDate":"2022-04-08T12:24:00.23","modifiedByFull":"Fitzgerald, Ethan","remark":"Mongstad port costs up 10k"},{"modifiedDate":"2022-04-05T12:37:00.69","modifiedByFull":"Fitzgerald, Ethan","remark":"TCE in line with estimate, 4 additional ports were covered by the LS payments given vessel\u2019s hire rate. TCPs optional 12 month period went into effect 07 March thus the $15k expense in VMS adjusting for this updated rate. Marquis requested speed up to Rotterdam which went smooth for 8 days before vessel forced to reduced and allow 7m swells to pass in front. Operationally, head owners made this one a bit difficult in Mongstad as they required a reissue of BL after blending with gasoline. The discussion lasted until a couple days before arrival when Marquis finally agreed to reissue, per agreed term in COA. Further bunker barge was delayed in Amsterdam which forced us to cancel the stem, luckily for no cancellation costs but LSMGO in Mongstad was $200/mt more expensive, vessel arrived with 43 mt ROB. 1600 MT overage adds $52k to freight and final demurrage claim accounts for 4.25 days. Note worthy is vessel spent 45H under pilot during this voyage."},{"modifiedDate":"2022-03-29T21:05:26.23","modifiedByFull":"Fitzgerald, Ethan","remark":"vessel lost time during transatlantic transit to allow storm to pass (reviewing) / accounting for river transits - in total about 45H under pilot"},{"modifiedDate":"2022-03-09T21:05:51.837","modifiedByFull":"Fitzgerald, Ethan","remark":"bunker barge unable to attend on schedule in Amsterdam, given turnaround switching to Mongstad"},{"modifiedDate":"2022-03-02T22:11:38.06","modifiedByFull":"Fitzgerald, Ethan","remark":"1,600 MT overage adds 52k to freight"},{"modifiedDate":"2022-03-02T19:27:08.173","modifiedByFull":"Fitzgerald, Ethan","remark":"laytime = 11.6 days total"},{"modifiedDate":"2022-02-24T21:46:38.013","modifiedByFull":"Fitzgerald, Ethan","remark":"Hire rate increases to $15,500/day on 9th March"}],"offhireList":[{"id":190354,"dateStartUtc":null,"dateEndUtc":null,"days":null,"displayOrder":0,"offhireReason":null,"remark":null,"offhireBunkerList":[{"id":47913,"gradeName":"LSBF","quantity":null,"price":null,"displayOrder":0}]}],"tcNumber":null,"tcOutIdEncrypted":null,"tcReletDetail":null}